pped with  or more gears in  mack offers three engine series the  l mp   l mp and  l mp with  hp  kw to  hp  kw and  lb·ft  n·m to  lb·ft  n·m     other productsedit mack also produced railroad cars and locomotives between  and  trademarkedit the companys trademark is the bulldog which can be found on the front of almost all mack trucks a goldplated bulldog indicates the truck was made with a mack produced drive train of engine transmission and drive axles a chrome bulldog indicates other manufacturers components were usedcitation needed mack trucks earned their nickname during world war i when the british government purchased the mack ac for supplying its front lines its pugnacious bluntnosed hood tenacious performance and incredible durability reminded the soldiers of their countrys mascot the british bulldog the logo was first used in  for the ab chain drive models and became the official corporate logo in  leadershipedit this is a list of the highest ranking executive officer of mack trucks since its inception mack leader dates of service john m mack  to  and  to october   otto mears april   to january   jacob sulzbach january   to january   thomas rush january   to december   charles p coleman october   to june   john calder june to october  vernon munroe october   to may   alfred j brosseau may   to september   emil c fink january   to january   charles t ruhf august   to june   edwin d bransome june   to january   peter o peterson january   to december   christian a johnson  to  acting president nicholas dykstra july   to september   c rhoades mcbride september   to january   zenon cr hansen january   to january   henry j nave january   to january   alfred w pelletier january   to july   john b curcio july   to  ralph reins  to  elios pascual  to  pierre jocou march   to november   michel gigou december   to july   paul vikner july   to april   dennis slagle april   to january   kevin flaherty january   to january   stephen roy january   to march   dennis sla